WATCH ME is the result of a remarkable creative alliance between Brazilian Leo Oliver and Italian Lollow.
Drawing from their diverse backgrounds, Leo Oliver and Lollow seamlessly weaved their unique styles and influences into the track. While Leo’s Miami roots infused the piece with the vibrant and pulsating energy of the city’s electronic music scene, Lollow’s signature elements from his previous tracks left their mark, enriching WATCH ME with a sense of familiarity and evolution. On August 04th available in all major platforms.
